metadata.name: nFt
metadata.description:
1st art piece of collection NFTID

Uniqueness that moves - this is how we define nFt. 
We have used our long experience in visual identity/Communication to create a unique symbol, the wordmark nFt was created only with rotation of a one letter. 
A symbol created in this way takes less space in brain.
Symbol is made of 10 dots/pixels to emphasize the binary (0 and 1)

nFt - in which rotation of literally 1 letter - n gives us a wordmark, ironizing those collections, which generate thousands of files actually of the same art by randomizing its details.

Artwork by Irakli Dolidze.
2160x2160, 60 FPS, MP4.
idolize, 2022
